ï¼ Pragya - could you do the following:

1. Open Preferences > Titanium Studio > Troubleshooting page, change Debug Level to "All" and make the com.aptana.core/debug/shell entry checked;
2. Restart Studio;
3. Run packaging on Mobile Web again to generate the error;
4. Attach the Studio log via Help > Titanium Studio > View Log File.

Also you could try running the same command you see in the log from the command line to see if it returns the same error.

Thanks.
